## 7. ⚙️ Working of the Application

* The GUI allows users to input a URL
* When the "Summarize" button is clicked:

  * The article is fetched
  * Text is analyzed
  * Summary is generated
* The result is displayed instantly
* The "Clear" button resets all fields

